<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3836778>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Psammoecus grandis Grouvelle, 1908. A. Right antenna. B. Median lobe. C. Parameres. Scale lines = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3836778/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3836776>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Psammoecus procerus sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus. B. Head. C. Pronotum. D. Right antenna. E–G. Aedeagus (E = ventral, F = lateral, G = dorsal view). Scale lines: A = 1.0 mm, B–G = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3836776/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3836780>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Psammoecus sinuaticollis sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus. B. Head and pronotum. C. Right antenna. D–F. Aedeagus (D = ventral, E = lateral, F = dorsal view). Scale lines: A = 1.0 mm, B–C = 0.5 mm, D–F = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3836780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3836774>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Psammoecus luchti Karner, 2012. A. Median lobe. B. Parameres. Scale lines = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3836774/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3836772>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Psammoecus nyakabuyensis sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus. B. Head. C. Pronotum. D. Right antenna. E. Aedeagus, ventral view. F. Paramere, lateral view. G. Median lobe, lateral view. Scale lines: A = 1.0 mm, B–D = 0.5 mm, E–G = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3836772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

